{"tid":381811,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷舊/拋磚引玉]一人幾首有成三四十年歷史但係放到依家仲係非常好聽既歌","createTime":"2017-08-31T09:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T17:45:00.000Z","uid":41375,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe145658709a8fe97349172bf3e601b12251534","tid":381811,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"Suzanne Vega - luka (1986)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VZt7J0iaUD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVZt7J0iaUD0&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8b0caa50\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VZt7J0iaUD0</a><br />\n唔好以為首歌聽落好似好輕鬆就以為係d正能量歌或者係d普通情歌 其實首歌係講虐待兒童 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFra Lippo Lippi - shouldn't have to be like that (1986）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dQ3FnqaSLsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdQ3FnqaSLsc&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=34ab537c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dQ3FnqaSLsc</a><br />\n前奏好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe rolling stones - gimme shelter （1969）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R3rnxQBizoU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR3rnxQBizoU&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f6f9d094\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R3rnxQBizoU</a><br />\n依首我估好多人都識 不過要用電腦先聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用手機youtube搵其他版本都唔係咁好聽"},{"pid":"2f32bce0190771d479560fd0082c37d64a312885","tid":381811,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"日文英文廣東話咩語言都冇所謂 只要好聽就得"},{"pid":"568a38580424dec7040339156bdf036f0361684f","tid":381811,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"Gimme shelter其實聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\