yTime":"2017-08-31T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"其實我個標題既意思唔係咁準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該係話&quot;雖然已經推出左幾十年但係依家聽返都唔會覺得老土/過時/冇咩時代感既歌&quot;先啱"},{"pid":"f8df425fbe44df8cd4efe2a840e2d0bd67a4b031","tid":381811,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我個標題既意思唔係咁準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該係話&quot;雖然已經推出左幾十年但係依家聽返都唔會覺得老土/過時/冇咩時代感既歌&quot;先啱</blockquote><br />\n又或者叫前衛都可以"},{"pid":"f08041e287a68cbe2afa38338e0071d850be74b2","tid":381811,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:48:03.000Z","msg":"The Beatles既歌永遠唔會老土<br />\nbtw 對我嚟講所有progressive rock 同 psychedelic rock 既歌都聽唔厭"},{"pid":"a19755d2f9b9a070b23399e71ca3f1f1ab19d745","tid":381811,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The Beatles既歌永遠唔會老土<br />\nbtw 對我嚟講所有progressive rock 同 psychedelic rock 既歌都聽唔厭</blockquote><br />\n其實好多六七十年代的音樂依家聽返都唔會覺得老土 反而仲會覺得好前衛<br />\n 好似Tangerine Dream, Jean-Michel Jarre依D composer 70年代既作品咁 依家聽返都完全唔覺得老土 反而會覺得好有未來感同科技感 當然入唔入口就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我既標題用前衛黎形容其實都唔係好正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係話仲仍然符合現代大眾人口味 易入口先啱"},{"pid":"43d59f0b07c85be5bea859b41960e9062bfe9bfe","tid":381811,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"Hotel California"},{"pid":"5fe8429783402ef81e1c449c55a16c4fbd155908","tid":381811,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>The Beatles既歌永遠唔會老土<br />\nbtw 對我嚟講所有progressive rock 同 psychedelic rock 既歌都聽唔厭</blockquote><br />\n其實好多六七十年代的音樂依家聽返都唔會覺得老土 反而仲會覺得好前衛<br />\n 好似Tangerine Dream, Jean-Michel Jarre依D composer 70年代既作品咁 依家聽返都完全唔覺得老土 反而會覺得好有未來感同科技感 當然入唔入口就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我既標題用前衛黎形容其實都唔係好正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係話仲仍然符合現代大眾人口味 易入口先啱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我認同係音樂上新不如舊<br />\n舊時既音樂百家爭鳴,現時我覺得無咩歌能經過時間洗禮"},{"pid":"b8b44c63a560c717925256f95a62f40565162480","tid":381811,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>The Beatles既歌永遠唔會老土<br />\nbtw 對我嚟講所有progressive rock 同 psychedelic rock 既歌都聽唔厭</blockquote><br />\n其實好多六七十年代的音樂依家聽返都唔會覺得老土 反而仲會覺得好前衛<br />\n 好似Tangerine Dream, Jean-Michel Jarre依D composer 70年代既作品咁 依家聽返都完全唔覺得老土 反而會覺得好有未來感同科技感 當然入唔入口就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我既標題用前衛黎形容其實都唔係好正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係話仲仍然符合現代大眾人口味 易入口先啱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我認同係音樂上新不如舊<br />\n舊時既音樂百家爭鳴,現時我覺得無咩歌能經過時間洗禮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現時既音樂係易入口,但係好似會過期"},{"pid":"56e056674bc0212777189a3e61dcb99bd4ef7f29","tid":381811,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"陳百強- 等 ，長伴千世紀"},{"pid":"27896b2514cc8ebf98c7ce19924731465ea5fb75","tid":381811,"uid":11285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"eternal flame"},{"pid":"17aad501c00d7cf6aa20208578699466da12b702","tid":381811,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fca3cf0f3b014a06c3f0dc7ea794e39bd6f516fa","tid":381811,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f61d5e69f389a31de05b2e4f6cdb469167e0d3d","tid":381811,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"Dancing in the moonlight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過係因為細個睇YouTube踢波片首歌係其中一首backtrack <br />\n唔知點解聽完就一直都好鐘意<br />\n原版係King Harvest <br />\n但係我聽嗰個版本係Toploader<br />\n兩個都好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}